<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="春日影 (MyGO!!!!! ver.)"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="MyGO!!!!!"/><amll:meta key="album" value="迷跡波"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPR562300280"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1783644617"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2097486090"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="2GC2OsWhRm9ltfxWBKuHhE"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="004Fy3wu3A1gHG"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="443654270"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="50747104"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="Xionghaizi001"/></metadata></head><body dur="4:12.160"><div begin="15.260" end="4:12.160"><p begin="15.260" end="19.160" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="15.260" end="15.750">悴</span><span begin="15.750" end="15.910">ん</span><span begin="15.910" end="16.080">だ</span><span begin="16.200" end="17.050">心</span> <span begin="17.160" end="17.430">ふ</span><span begin="17.470" end="17.680">る</span><span begin="17.770" end="18.040">え</span><span begin="18.060" end="18.170">る</span><span begin="18.240" end="18.630">眼</span><span begin="18.660" end="18.900">差</span><span begin="18.950" end="19.160">し</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">内心满是憔悴 眼神颤抖不止</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음은 초췌해지고 눈빛은 하염없이 떨려</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Numb heart a trembling gaze</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kajikanda kokoro furueru manazashi</span></p><p begin="19.240" end="25.440" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.240" end="19.860">世</span><span begin="19.920" end="20.190">界</span><span begin="20.240" end="21.160">で</span> <span begin="22.090" end="22.660">僕</span><span begin="22.660" end="22.830">は</span> <span begin="22.850" end="22.940">ひ</span><span begin="23.020" end="23.580">と</span><span begin="23.640" end="23.860">り</span><span begin="23.950" end="24.460">ぼ</span><span begin="24.460" end="24.540">っ</span><span begin="24.540" end="24.790">ち</span><span begin="24.880" end="25.130">だ</span><span begin="25.130" end="25.210">っ</span><span begin="25.210" end="25.440">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我在这世界孤独一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 이 세상에 홀로 남겨졌어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In this world I was all alone</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sekai de boku wa hitoribocchi datta</span></p><p begin="25.760" end="31.340" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.760" end="26.080">散</span><span begin="26.110" end="26.310">る</span><span begin="26.420" end="26.600">こ</span><span begin="26.740" end="27.240">と</span><span begin="27.300" end="27.520">し</span><span begin="27.670" end="27.920">か</span><span begin="28.240" end="28.500">知</span><span begin="28.580" end="28.880">ら</span><span begin="28.900" end="29.150">な</span><span begin="29.200" end="29.390">い</span><span begin="29.490" end="30.380">春</span><span begin="30.440" end="31.340">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在不断凋零的春季中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끊임없이 시들어가는 봄 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The spring that only knows how to fall</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Chiru koto shika shiranai haru wa</span></p><p begin="31.960" end="36.920" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.960" end="32.490">毎</span><span begin="32.600" end="33.120">年</span> <span begin="33.200" end="33.740">冷</span><span begin="33.850" end="34.060">た</span><span begin="34.140" end="34.660">く</span><span begin="34.760" end="34.980">あ</span><span begin="35.020" end="35.670">し</span><span begin="35.700" end="35.950">ら</span><span begin="36.030" end="36.920">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">每年都只感受到冰冷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">매년 차가움만을 느낄 뿐이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Coldly treats me every year</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Maitoshi tsumetaku ashirau</span></p><p begin="37.520" end="41.460" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="37.520" end="37.830">暗</span><span begin="37.870" end="38.170">が</span><span begin="38.200" end="38.430">り</span><span begin="38.490" end="38.730">の</span><span begin="38.800" end="39.390">中</span> <span begin="39.430" end="39.580">一</span><span begin="39.720" end="40.210">方</span><span begin="40.300" end="40.550">通</span><span begin="40.640" end="41.240">行</span><span begin="41.260" end="41.460">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在一片黑暗中 单向往前走着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어둠 속에서 일방통행으로 나아가며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In the darkness on a one-way street</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuragari no naka ippoutsuukou ni</span></p><p begin="41.580" end="47.720" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.580" end="42.150">た</span><span begin="42.200" end="42.290">だ</span> <span begin="42.350" end="42.460">た</span><span begin="42.510" end="43.860">だ</span> <span begin="44.330" end="44.920">言</span><span begin="44.980" end="45.220">葉</span><span begin="45.290" end="45.830">を</span><span begin="45.900" end="46.120">書</span><span begin="46.220" end="46.800">き</span><span begin="46.830" end="47.430">殴</span><span begin="47.430" end="47.480">っ</span><span begin="47.480" end="47.720">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我只能不断胡乱写着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 그저 마구 적어 내려갈 뿐이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just simply scribbling down words</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tada tada kotoba o kakinagutte</span></p><p begin="48.040" end="55.080" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.040" end="48.280">期</span><span begin="48.380" end="48.880">待</span><span begin="48.940" end="49.290">す</span><span begin="49.310" end="49.600">る</span><span begin="49.620" end="49.790">だ</span><span begin="49.910" end="50.240">け</span> <span begin="50.560" end="50.800">む</span><span begin="50.880" end="51.100">な</span><span begin="51.150" end="51.460">し</span><span begin="51.460" end="51.680">い</span><span begin="51.790" end="52.340">と</span><span begin="52.400" end="52.560">分</span><span begin="52.700" end="54.070">か</span><span begin="54.070" end="54.260">っ</span><span begin="54.260" end="54.390">て</span><span begin="54.390" end="54.470">い</span><span begin="54.570" end="54.830">て</span><span begin="54.880" end="55.080">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明知期待也是一场空</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기대해 보아도 헛수고라는 걸 알면서도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even knowing that merely hoping is in vain</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kitai suru dake munashii to wakatte itemo</span></p><p begin="55.430" end="59.440" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="55.430" end="56.120">救</span><span begin="56.120" end="56.370">い</span><span begin="56.430" end="56.670">を</span><span begin="56.740" end="56.980">求</span><span begin="57.040" end="57.130">め</span><span begin="57.180" end="57.870">続</span><span begin="57.950" end="58.170">け</span><span begin="58.280" end="59.440">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">却依然不断寻求救赎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여전히 끊임없이 구원을 찾았어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I continued to seek salvation</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sukui o motometsuzuketa</span></p><p begin="1:00.070" end="1:03.360" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:00.070" end="1:00.340">せ</span><span begin="1:00.420" end="1:00.710">つ</span><span begin="1:00.750" end="1:00.960">な</span><span begin="1:01.040" end="1:01.260">く</span><span begin="1:01.370" end="1:01.660">て</span> <span begin="1:01.660" end="1:01.890">い</span><span begin="1:01.990" end="1:02.260">と</span><span begin="1:02.260" end="1:02.470">お</span><span begin="1:02.550" end="1:02.950">し</span><span begin="1:02.950" end="1:03.360">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">令人揪心又令人心爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애가 타면서도 사랑스러워</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Heartbreaking yet precious</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Setsunakute itooshii</span></p><p begin="1:03.520" end="1:07.360" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.520" end="1:04.110">今</span><span begin="1:04.150" end="1:04.270">な</span><span begin="1:04.290" end="1:04.430">ら</span><span begin="1:04.470" end="1:04.700">ば</span> <span begin="1:04.760" end="1:04.990">分</span><span begin="1:05.080" end="1:05.370">か</span><span begin="1:05.400" end="1:05.590">る</span><span begin="1:05.680" end="1:06.250">気</span><span begin="1:06.310" end="1:06.390">が</span><span begin="1:06.440" end="1:06.600">す</span><span begin="1:06.620" end="1:07.360">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是如今 好像已经明白</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금이라면 왠지 알 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I feel like I understand it now</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima naraba wakaru ki ga suru</span></p><p begin="1:07.520" end="1:10.800" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:07.520" end="1:07.880">し</span><span begin="1:07.880" end="1:08.130">あ</span><span begin="1:08.190" end="1:08.370">わ</span><span begin="1:08.460" end="1:08.740">せ</span><span begin="1:08.790" end="1:08.990">で</span> <span begin="1:09.080" end="1:09.380">く</span><span begin="1:09.410" end="1:09.680">る</span><span begin="1:09.680" end="1:09.860">お</span><span begin="1:09.980" end="1:10.390">し</span><span begin="1:10.390" end="1:10.800">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">幸福却又让人心乱神迷</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">행복하면서도 마음을 어지럽게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Happy yet maddening</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shiawase de kuruoshii</span></p><p begin="1:10.940" end="1:14.520" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.940" end="1:11.200">あ</span><span begin="1:11.270" end="1:11.510">の</span><span begin="1:11.550" end="1:11.680">日</span><span begin="1:11.730" end="1:11.810">泣</span><span begin="1:11.870" end="1:11.990">け</span><span begin="1:12.020" end="1:12.130">な</span><span begin="1:12.190" end="1:12.500">か</span><span begin="1:12.500" end="1:12.720">っ</span><span begin="1:12.820" end="1:13.020">た</span><span begin="1:13.100" end="1:13.980">僕</span><span begin="1:14.050" end="1:14.520">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">照耀着无法哭泣的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">울지 못하던 나를 비추며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The me who couldn&apos;t cry that day</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ano hi nakenakatta boku o</span></p><p begin="1:14.670" end="1:21.460" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.670" end="1:15.810">光</span><span begin="1:15.910" end="1:16.820">は</span> <span begin="1:17.460" end="1:17.690">や</span><span begin="1:17.730" end="1:17.990">さ</span><span begin="1:18.010" end="1:18.270">し</span><span begin="1:18.370" end="1:18.450">く</span><span begin="1:18.510" end="1:18.660">連</span><span begin="1:18.690" end="1:19.520">れ</span><span begin="1:19.630" end="1:19.700">立</span><span begin="1:19.760" end="1:19.880">つ</span><span begin="1:19.920" end="1:21.460">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">光芒温柔地携我同行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">빛이 다정하게 나와 함께 걸어줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The light gently accompanies me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hikari wa yasashiku tsuredatsu yo</span></p><p begin="1:22.350" end="1:25.570" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:22.350" end="1:22.650">雲</span><span begin="1:22.720" end="1:22.860">間</span><span begin="1:22.860" end="1:22.970">を</span><span begin="1:23.020" end="1:23.250">ぬ</span><span begin="1:23.250" end="1:23.340">っ</span><span begin="1:23.340" end="1:23.720">て</span> <span begin="1:23.940" end="1:24.040">き</span><span begin="1:24.070" end="1:24.220">ら</span><span begin="1:24.260" end="1:24.560">り</span><span begin="1:24.890" end="1:25.000">き</span><span begin="1:25.020" end="1:25.170">ら</span><span begin="1:25.190" end="1:25.570">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">穿过层层云朵 变得闪闪发光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">겹겹의 구름을 뚫고 반짝반짝 빛나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Slipping through the clouds twinkling twinkling</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kumoma o nutte kirari kirari</span></p><p begin="1:25.810" end="1:29.350" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:25.810" end="1:26.760">心</span><span begin="1:26.890" end="1:26.980">満</span><span begin="1:27.040" end="1:27.250">た</span><span begin="1:27.300" end="1:27.550">し</span><span begin="1:27.670" end="1:27.860">て</span><span begin="1:27.970" end="1:28.380">は</span> <span begin="1:28.610" end="1:28.860">溢</span><span begin="1:28.910" end="1:29.350">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">内心的思绪满溢而出</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음속 생각들이 흘러넘쳐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Filling the heart and overflowing</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro mitashite wa afure</span></p><p begin="1:29.810" end="1:33.050" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.810" end="1:29.890">い</span><span begin="1:29.970" end="1:30.040">つ</span><span begin="1:30.090" end="1:30.200">し</span><span begin="1:30.280" end="1:30.400">か</span><span begin="1:30.460" end="1:30.900">頬</span><span begin="1:30.900" end="1:31.110">を</span> <span begin="1:31.350" end="1:31.470">き</span><span begin="1:31.480" end="1:31.640">ら</span><span begin="1:31.680" end="1:31.990">り</span><span begin="1:32.290" end="1:32.400">き</span><span begin="1:32.420" end="1:32.570">ら</span><span begin="1:32.600" end="1:33.050">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">脸颊回过神来 也正闪闪发光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느새 뺨도 반짝반짝 빛나고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Before I knew it on my cheeks twinkling twinkling</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsushika hoho o kirari kirari</span></p><p begin="1:33.370" end="1:36.640" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.370" end="1:33.750">熱</span><span begin="1:33.850" end="1:34.060">く</span> <span begin="1:34.320" end="1:34.680">熱</span><span begin="1:34.770" end="1:35.050">く</span><span begin="1:35.080" end="1:35.350">濡</span><span begin="1:35.390" end="1:35.870">ら</span><span begin="1:35.880" end="1:35.960">し</span><span begin="1:36.010" end="1:36.180">て</span><span begin="1:36.180" end="1:36.270">ゆ</span><span begin="1:36.340" end="1:36.640">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">热泪沾湿了我的脸庞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뜨거운 눈물이 내 뺨을 적셔가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hotly hotly wetting them</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Atsuku atsuku nurashite yuku</span></p><p begin="1:36.920" end="1:44.070" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.920" end="1:37.220">君</span><span begin="1:37.250" end="1:37.760">の</span><span begin="1:37.870" end="1:38.120">手</span><span begin="1:38.170" end="1:38.620">は</span> <span begin="1:38.800" end="1:39.010">ど</span><span begin="1:39.110" end="1:39.580">う</span><span begin="1:39.660" end="1:39.930">し</span><span begin="1:40.030" end="1:40.330">て</span><span begin="1:40.650" end="1:40.800">こ</span><span begin="1:40.800" end="1:40.960">ん</span><span begin="1:40.960" end="1:41.540">な</span><span begin="1:41.570" end="1:41.800">に</span><span begin="1:41.890" end="1:42.200">も</span><span begin="1:42.520" end="1:43.200">温</span><span begin="1:43.270" end="1:43.460">か</span><span begin="1:43.460" end="1:43.680">い</span><span begin="1:43.750" end="1:44.040">の</span><span begin="1:44.040" end="1:44.070">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么你的手是如此地温暖？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어째서 네 손은 이토록이나 따스한 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why are your hands so warm?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no te wa doushite konna ni mo atatakai no?</span></p><p begin="1:44.360" end="1:46.080" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.360" end="1:44.560">ねぇ</span><span begin="1:44.660" end="1:45.240">お</span><span begin="1:45.290" end="1:46.080">願い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 拜托你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저기 부탁이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey I beg you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee onegai</span></p><p begin="1:46.210" end="1:53.580" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:46.210" end="1:46.440">ど</span><span begin="1:46.530" end="1:47.030">う</span><span begin="1:47.140" end="1:47.330">か</span><span begin="1:47.460" end="1:47.720">こ</span><span begin="1:47.770" end="1:48.020">の</span><span begin="1:48.070" end="1:48.230">ま</span><span begin="1:48.400" end="1:49.310">ま</span> <span begin="1:50.200" end="1:50.730">離</span><span begin="1:50.810" end="1:51.070">さ</span><span begin="1:51.160" end="1:51.470">な</span><span begin="1:51.510" end="1:51.740">い</span><span begin="1:51.780" end="1:51.900">で</span><span begin="1:51.900" end="1:51.990">い</span><span begin="1:52.090" end="1:53.580">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请你从此再也不要放手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부디 이대로 다시는 놓지 말아 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Please don&apos;t let go just like this</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Douka kono mama hanasanaide ite</span></p><p begin="1:55.490" end="1:59.400" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.490" end="1:55.830">縁</span><span begin="1:55.830" end="1:56.060">を</span><span begin="1:56.120" end="1:56.630">結</span><span begin="1:56.740" end="1:57.040">ん</span><span begin="1:57.040" end="1:57.300">で</span><span begin="1:57.340" end="1:57.580">は</span> <span begin="1:57.670" end="1:57.920">ほ</span><span begin="1:57.970" end="1:58.160">ど</span><span begin="1:58.260" end="1:58.350">き</span><span begin="1:58.400" end="1:58.520">ほ</span><span begin="1:58.610" end="1:58.830">ど</span><span begin="1:58.920" end="1:59.170">か</span><span begin="1:59.210" end="1:59.400">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">人与人的缘分 总是断断续续</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사람과 사람의 인연은 늘 끊어졌다 이어지고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Tying bonds untying and being untied</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">En o musunde wa hodoki hodokare</span></p><p begin="1:59.500" end="2:07.190" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.500" end="2:00.050">誰</span><span begin="2:00.120" end="2:00.230">し</span><span begin="2:00.280" end="2:00.360">も</span><span begin="2:00.460" end="2:01.480">が</span><span begin="2:02.270" end="2:02.590">そ</span><span begin="2:02.600" end="2:02.860">れ</span><span begin="2:02.910" end="2:03.140">を</span><span begin="2:03.180" end="2:04.720">喜</span><span begin="2:04.780" end="2:04.970">び</span> <span begin="2:05.070" end="2:05.320">悲</span><span begin="2:05.380" end="2:05.630">し</span><span begin="2:06.010" end="2:06.240">み</span><span begin="2:06.330" end="2:06.500">な</span><span begin="2:06.620" end="2:06.860">が</span><span begin="2:06.950" end="2:07.190">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">人们在喜悦及悲伤中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">사람들은 기쁨과 슬픔 속에서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">While everyone finds joy and sorrow in it</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dareshimo ga sore o yorokobi kanashimi nagara</span></p><p begin="2:07.240" end="2:11.670" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.240" end="2:07.760">愛</span><span begin="2:07.870" end="2:08.250">を</span><span begin="2:08.780" end="2:09.390">数</span><span begin="2:09.390" end="2:09.610">え</span><span begin="2:09.720" end="2:10.250">て</span><span begin="2:10.330" end="2:10.530">ゆ</span><span begin="2:10.620" end="2:11.670">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">细数一个又一个的爱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하나둘 사랑을 헤아려 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">We go on counting love</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ai o kazoete yuku</span></p><p begin="2:12.180" end="2:17.450" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.180" end="2:12.310">鼓</span><span begin="2:12.350" end="2:12.770">動</span><span begin="2:12.830" end="2:13.050">を</span><span begin="2:13.440" end="2:13.960">確</span><span begin="2:14.070" end="2:14.270">か</span><span begin="2:14.370" end="2:14.950">め</span><span begin="2:14.990" end="2:15.260">る</span><span begin="2:15.300" end="2:15.850">よ</span><span begin="2:15.930" end="2:16.160">う</span><span begin="2:16.230" end="2:17.450">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为了确认内心的跳动</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음의 고동을 확인하듯이</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if to confirm our heartbeats</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kodou o tashikameru you ni</span></p><p begin="2:18.060" end="2:21.420" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:18.060" end="2:18.360">う</span><span begin="2:18.380" end="2:18.580">れ</span><span begin="2:18.650" end="2:18.860">し</span><span begin="2:18.980" end="2:19.200">く</span><span begin="2:19.310" end="2:19.470">て</span> <span begin="2:19.570" end="2:19.860">さ</span><span begin="2:19.940" end="2:20.110">び</span><span begin="2:20.210" end="2:20.420">し</span><span begin="2:20.520" end="2:20.720">く</span><span begin="2:20.850" end="2:21.420">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">令人喜悦却又叫人寂寞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기쁘면서도 외롭게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So glad yet so lonely</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ureshikute sabishikute</span></p><p begin="2:21.450" end="2:25.160" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.450" end="2:22.050">今</span><span begin="2:22.080" end="2:22.170">だ</span><span begin="2:22.250" end="2:22.390">か</span><span begin="2:22.410" end="2:22.630">ら</span> <span begin="2:22.710" end="2:22.940">分</span><span begin="2:23.020" end="2:23.310">か</span><span begin="2:23.330" end="2:23.530">る</span><span begin="2:23.630" end="2:24.160">気</span><span begin="2:24.250" end="2:24.340">が</span><span begin="2:24.390" end="2:24.540">し</span><span begin="2:24.580" end="2:25.160">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻感觉好像能了解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금이라면 왠지 알 수 있을 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I felt like I understood because it&apos;s now</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima dakara wakaru ki ga shita</span></p><p begin="2:25.490" end="2:28.860" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:25.490" end="2:25.820">た</span><span begin="2:25.820" end="2:26.010">い</span><span begin="2:26.060" end="2:26.310">せ</span><span begin="2:26.410" end="2:26.690">つ</span><span begin="2:26.740" end="2:26.930">で</span> <span begin="2:27.030" end="2:27.320">こ</span><span begin="2:27.360" end="2:27.560">わ</span><span begin="2:27.650" end="2:28.080">く</span><span begin="2:28.080" end="2:28.280">っ</span><span begin="2:28.280" end="2:28.860">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">重要却又让人感到害怕</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">소중하면서도 두렵게 해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So precious yet so scary</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taisetsu de kowakutte</span></p><p begin="2:28.890" end="2:32.470" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:28.890" end="2:29.090">あ</span><span begin="2:29.210" end="2:29.440">の</span><span begin="2:29.480" end="2:29.610">日</span><span begin="2:29.640" end="2:29.730">泣</span><span begin="2:29.800" end="2:29.910">け</span><span begin="2:29.950" end="2:30.050">な</span><span begin="2:30.120" end="2:30.420">か</span><span begin="2:30.420" end="2:30.630">っ</span><span begin="2:30.750" end="2:30.980">た</span><span begin="2:31.060" end="2:31.940">僕</span><span begin="2:31.990" end="2:32.470">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">照耀着无法哭泣的我</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">울지 못하던 나를 비추며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The me who couldn&apos;t cry that day</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ano hi nakenakatta boku o</span></p><p begin="2:32.610" end="2:39.710" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:32.610" end="2:33.770">光</span><span begin="2:33.850" end="2:34.890">は</span> <span begin="2:35.390" end="2:35.640">や</span><span begin="2:35.680" end="2:35.940">さ</span><span begin="2:35.980" end="2:36.220">し</span><span begin="2:36.330" end="2:36.420">く</span><span begin="2:36.440" end="2:36.540">抱</span><span begin="2:36.620" end="2:37.400">き</span><span begin="2:37.510" end="2:37.640">し</span><span begin="2:37.700" end="2:37.800">め</span><span begin="2:37.890" end="2:39.710">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是光芒温柔地将我拥入怀中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">빛이 다정하게 나를 품에 안아주었어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The light gently embraced me</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hikari wa yasashiku dakishimeta</span></p><p begin="2:55.170" end="3:00.890" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:55.170" end="2:55.340">照</span><span begin="2:55.340" end="2:55.440">ら</span><span begin="2:55.470" end="2:55.630">さ</span><span begin="2:55.630" end="2:55.740">れ</span><span begin="2:55.800" end="2:55.890">た</span><span begin="2:55.920" end="2:56.040">世</span><span begin="2:56.110" end="2:56.700">界</span> <span begin="2:57.020" end="2:57.140">咲</span><span begin="2:57.220" end="2:57.300">き</span><span begin="2:57.330" end="2:57.650">誇</span><span begin="2:57.650" end="2:57.750">る</span><span begin="2:57.810" end="2:58.200">大</span><span begin="2:58.250" end="2:58.720">切</span><span begin="2:58.740" end="2:58.840">な</span><span begin="2:58.910" end="3:00.890">人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这阳光普照的世界 骄傲绽放的重要之人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">햇살 비치는 이 세상에서 자랑스럽게 피어난 소중한 사람</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The illuminated world the precious person blooming proudly</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Terasareta sekai sakihokoru taisetsu na hito</span></p><p begin="3:02.600" end="3:04.900" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:02.600" end="3:02.690">あ</span><span begin="3:02.760" end="3:02.860">た</span><span begin="3:02.920" end="3:03.000">た</span><span begin="3:03.080" end="3:03.160">か</span><span begin="3:03.210" end="3:03.360">さ</span><span begin="3:03.360" end="3:03.450">を</span><span begin="3:03.500" end="3:03.690">知</span><span begin="3:03.690" end="3:03.850">っ</span><span begin="3:03.850" end="3:04.180">た</span><span begin="3:04.480" end="3:04.730">春</span><span begin="3:04.760" end="3:04.900">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">知晓何谓温暖的春天</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">따스함이 무엇인지 알게 된 봄은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The spring that has come to know warmth</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Atatakasa o shitta haru wa</span></p><p begin="3:04.920" end="3:10.590" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:04.920" end="3:05.200">僕</span><span begin="3:05.220" end="3:05.320">の</span><span begin="3:05.400" end="3:05.660">た</span><span begin="3:05.700" end="3:05.900">め</span> <span begin="3:06.000" end="3:06.300">君</span><span begin="3:06.330" end="3:06.480">の</span><span begin="3:06.630" end="3:06.880">た</span><span begin="3:06.940" end="3:07.160">め</span><span begin="3:07.260" end="3:07.680">の</span> <span begin="3:08.170" end="3:08.730">涙</span><span begin="3:08.810" end="3:08.930">を</span><span begin="3:08.960" end="3:09.570">流</span><span begin="3:09.670" end="3:09.960">す</span><span begin="3:10.040" end="3:10.590">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为你我 而留下泪水</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너와 나를 위해 눈물을 흘려</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Will shed tears for me and for you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku no tame kimi no tame no namida o nagasu yo</span></p><p begin="3:10.950" end="3:13.390" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:10.950" end="3:11.230">あぁ</span> <span begin="3:11.270" end="3:11.380">な</span><span begin="3:11.380" end="3:11.590">ん</span><span begin="3:11.590" end="3:11.830">て</span><span begin="3:11.880" end="3:12.130">眩</span><span begin="3:12.180" end="3:12.440">し</span><span begin="3:12.500" end="3:12.640">い</span><span begin="3:12.640" end="3:12.790">ん</span><span begin="3:12.810" end="3:12.970">だ</span><span begin="3:12.970" end="3:13.180">ろ</span><span begin="3:13.180" end="3:13.390">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊啊 多么地耀眼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 얼마나 눈부신가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah how dazzling it is</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa nante mabushiindarou</span></p><p begin="3:14.660" end="3:21.110" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:14.660" end="3:14.940">あぁ</span> <span begin="3:14.980" end="3:15.150">な</span><span begin="3:15.150" end="3:15.290">ん</span><span begin="3:15.290" end="3:15.470">て</span><span begin="3:15.590" end="3:16.120">美</span><span begin="3:16.170" end="3:16.420">し</span><span begin="3:16.530" end="3:16.990">い</span><span begin="3:16.990" end="3:17.160">ん</span><span begin="3:17.160" end="3:17.400">だ</span><span begin="3:17.450" end="3:21.110">ろう…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊啊 多么地美丽…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 얼마나 아름다운가…</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah how beautiful it is…</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa nante utsukushiindarou…</span></p><p begin="3:32.230" end="3:35.430" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:32.230" end="3:32.540">雲</span><span begin="3:32.600" end="3:32.750">間</span><span begin="3:32.750" end="3:32.880">を</span><span begin="3:32.920" end="3:33.130">ぬ</span><span begin="3:33.130" end="3:33.240">っ</span><span begin="3:33.240" end="3:33.630">て</span> <span begin="3:33.840" end="3:33.970">き</span><span begin="3:34.000" end="3:34.140">ら</span><span begin="3:34.170" end="3:34.580">り</span><span begin="3:34.770" end="3:34.890">き</span><span begin="3:34.910" end="3:35.050">ら</span><span begin="3:35.090" end="3:35.430">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">穿过层层云朵 变得闪闪发光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">겹겹의 구름을 뚫고 반짝반짝 빛나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Slipping through the clouds twinkling twinkling</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kumoma o nutte kirari kirari</span></p><p begin="3:35.700" end="3:39.240" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:35.700" end="3:36.670">心</span><span begin="3:36.770" end="3:36.870">満</span><span begin="3:36.930" end="3:37.160">た</span><span begin="3:37.190" end="3:37.440">し</span><span begin="3:37.580" end="3:37.770">て</span><span begin="3:37.870" end="3:38.280">は</span> <span begin="3:38.490" end="3:38.740">溢</span><span begin="3:38.800" end="3:39.240">れ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">内心的思绪满溢而出</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음속 생각들이 흘러넘쳐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Filling the heart and overflowing</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro mitashite wa afure</span></p><p begin="3:39.700" end="3:42.880" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:39.700" end="3:39.800">い</span><span begin="3:39.860" end="3:39.940">つ</span><span begin="3:39.980" end="3:40.100">し</span><span begin="3:40.180" end="3:40.290">か</span><span begin="3:40.360" end="3:40.780">頬</span><span begin="3:40.780" end="3:41.020">を</span> <span begin="3:41.270" end="3:41.390">き</span><span begin="3:41.420" end="3:41.540">ら</span><span begin="3:41.580" end="3:41.910">り</span><span begin="3:42.190" end="3:42.310">き</span><span begin="3:42.340" end="3:42.460">ら</span><span begin="3:42.510" end="3:42.880">り</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">脸颊回过神来 也正闪闪发光</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어느새 뺨도 반짝반짝 빛나고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Before I knew it on my cheeks twinkling twinkling</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsushika hoho o kirari kirari</span></p><p begin="3:43.280" end="3:46.560" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:43.280" end="3:43.670">熱</span><span begin="3:43.760" end="3:43.990">く</span> <span begin="3:44.210" end="3:44.610">熱</span><span begin="3:44.680" end="3:44.930">く</span><span begin="3:44.980" end="3:45.230">濡</span><span begin="3:45.280" end="3:45.740">ら</span><span begin="3:45.770" end="3:45.850">し</span><span begin="3:45.900" end="3:46.080">て</span><span begin="3:46.080" end="3:46.160">ゆ</span><span begin="3:46.240" end="3:46.560">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">热泪沾湿了我的脸庞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">뜨거운 눈물이 내 뺨을 적셔가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hotly hotly wetting them</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Atsuku atsuku nurashite yuku</span></p><p begin="3:46.820" end="3:53.980" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:46.820" end="3:47.100">君</span><span begin="3:47.150" end="3:47.670">の</span><span begin="3:47.760" end="3:48.020">手</span><span begin="3:48.080" end="3:48.450">は</span> <span begin="3:48.690" end="3:48.890">ど</span><span begin="3:49.000" end="3:49.490">う</span><span begin="3:49.570" end="3:49.830">し</span><span begin="3:49.940" end="3:50.210">て</span><span begin="3:50.550" end="3:50.680">こ</span><span begin="3:50.680" end="3:50.850">ん</span><span begin="3:50.850" end="3:51.420">な</span><span begin="3:51.470" end="3:51.680">に</span><span begin="3:51.790" end="3:52.090">も</span><span begin="3:52.410" end="3:53.100">温</span><span begin="3:53.200" end="3:53.350">か</span><span begin="3:53.390" end="3:53.570">い</span><span begin="3:53.640" end="3:53.950">の</span><span begin="3:53.950" end="3:53.980">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">为什么你的手是如此地温暖？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어째서 네 손은 이토록이나 따스한 걸까?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Why are your hands so warm?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi no te wa doushite konna ni mo atatakai no?</span></p><p begin="3:54.240" end="3:56.000" itunes:key="L40" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:54.240" end="3:54.490">ねぇ</span><span begin="3:54.570" end="3:55.150">お</span><span begin="3:55.180" end="3:56.000">願い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 拜托你</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저기 부탁이야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey I beg you</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee onegai</span></p><p begin="3:56.110" end="4:03.000" itunes:key="L41" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:56.110" end="3:56.340">ど</span><span begin="3:56.430" end="3:56.900">う</span><span begin="3:57.050" end="3:57.240">か</span><span begin="3:57.350" end="3:57.630">こ</span><span begin="3:57.670" end="3:57.890">の</span><span begin="3:57.970" end="3:58.200">ま</span><span begin="3:58.280" end="3:59.140">ま</span> <span begin="4:00.120" end="4:00.610">離</span><span begin="4:00.690" end="4:00.940">さ</span><span begin="4:01.050" end="4:01.400">な</span><span begin="4:01.400" end="4:01.620">い</span><span begin="4:01.680" end="4:01.810">で</span><span begin="4:01.810" end="4:01.880">い</span><span begin="4:02.000" end="4:03.000">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请你从此再也不要放手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">부디 이대로 다시는 놓지 말아 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Please don&apos;t let go just like this</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Douka kono mama hanasanaide ite</span></p><p begin="4:03.830" end="4:12.160" itunes:key="L42" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4:03.830" end="4:03.960">ず</span><span begin="4:03.960" end="4:04.150">っ</span><span begin="4:04.150" end="4:04.440">と</span> <span begin="4:04.740" end="4:05.360">ず</span><span begin="4:05.360" end="4:05.520">っ</span><span begin="4:05.710" end="4:06.870">と</span> <span begin="4:07.560" end="4:08.070">離</span><span begin="4:08.140" end="4:08.410">さ</span><span begin="4:08.480" end="4:08.770">な</span><span begin="4:08.800" end="4:09.050">い</span><span begin="4:09.090" end="4:09.240">で</span><span begin="4:09.240" end="4:09.320">い</span><span begin="4:09.430" end="4:12.160">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">永远 永远 再也不要放手</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">영원히 영원히 다시는 놓지 말아 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Never ever let go</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zutto zutto hanasanaide ite</span></p></div></body></tt>